Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:40.36,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊擁抱 心靈的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:46.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情燃燒 創造奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:52.09,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣受著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:58.32,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相發誓過的 遙遠的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:04.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座的幻想 只有夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:10.60,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也奪不走 因為是心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:16.54,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 少年都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:20.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 明天的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:28.18,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 就像天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:35.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 現在就展開羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:35.01,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當邪惡在此世蔓延之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會現身的希望之戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身著星座之聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發蘊藏在身體中的能量「小宇宙」進行著戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正是 保護大地上愛與和平的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士光牙尋找雅典娜的旅程還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙一行人雖然破壞了雷之遺跡的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被來自其地下的謎樣黑暗所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在刻有「悔恨」「贖罪」的房間中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰 尤娜 榮斗同各自的過去進行了對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他們決心將過往的悔恨化為向未來前行的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將贖罪化作前進的動力之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一扇新的大門被打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年們 燃起內心的小宇宙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追憶與復仇！暗之遺跡的陷阱！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我是在雷之遺跡被黑暗所吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:02:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在那裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美狄亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問父親有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯大人如今仍在火星進行療養
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前暫無聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給父親這樣的強者造成如此重創
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個名為天馬座星矢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該說那些所謂的聖鬥士們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有著何等強大的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些擁有同我等火星士相抗衡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並與父親大人為敵的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受命代替瑪爾斯大人留守此處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能輕易擅離職守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故而對你有一事相托
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些忤逆瑪爾斯大人的聖鬥士之中的核心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是南十字座Southern Cross的一摩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去把他打倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也到了可以為瑪爾斯大人盡心盡力的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星士們也在期待著這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還很不成熟 難當此等重任…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說你我並無血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我從你幼年時就開始照料你 同你一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的實力 我美狄亞心知肚明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的能力 一定能完美地完成使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯大人也在期待著你的表現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:04:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親手打敗聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 您在修煉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以站在火星士的身後哦 伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能就這麼白白丟了性命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和您打個招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去見阿莉雅嗎 伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親說了 和阿莉雅做朋友不是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但走得太近也不是什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 您怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 您的小宇宙和平時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有些動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花要枯萎了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要外出數日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉暫時停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要出門嗎？去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸你不必知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是做夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的有聖鬥士被那黑暗勢力拉攏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說近來Palaestra裡發生的失蹤事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也和那些穿著紅黑盔甲的傢伙有關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一摩 就這麼放任那些傢伙為所欲為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士之間的羈絆就要四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你肯行動 我們就立刻跟隨你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不能正式行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機未到 尚需等待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲速則不達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須探清他們的底細再行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都這麼說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一摩的話不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該吃晚飯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你兒子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他叫蒼摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 叔叔你們是聖鬥士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們是白銀聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久的將來 我也要成為聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為雅典娜而戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 一摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在…看著過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這幅景像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚飯是茄汁雞肉哦 快回家開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 聽起來很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要離開一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你不吃茄汁雞肉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我等你回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 別去！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不正是那天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老爸失去性命的那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快去追老爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則老爸就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 老爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快現身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有事找我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子？從今早起一直在窺伺著我動向的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南十字星座 Southern Cross的一摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是索尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這忤逆瑪爾斯大人的聖鬥士 由我來打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你肯歸順瑪爾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放你一馬也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不和小鬼戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你這樣的小孩來做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愈發不能饒恕那個叫瑪爾斯的傢伙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至還未理解其意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這拳頭 應用於守護自己珍視之物才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍視的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯大人也在期待著你的表現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的小宇宙和平時不同 似乎有些動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯 索尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信你可以完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從第一次與年幼的你相遇開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便一直如此認為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回房去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好歇息吧 索尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你與聖鬥士交戰了 索尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時你在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有過迷惘 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女兒 伊甸的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應當理解我為什麼要創建新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼好猶豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉 下次決不會再發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得還會有下一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你這樣的懦弱之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯大人 請您原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我決不會再猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區聖鬥士 無論幾個人幾十個人我都會打倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不足為信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對於我與我的計劃而言毫無用處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所看到的一切 都是幻覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是由你的內心映射出的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為愛與憎恨的黑暗所束縛的人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體就給我一分為二吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是說這種話的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是我的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能殺死你的 只有南十字星座一摩的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幼獅座的蒼摩！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不准你擅自在這種地方死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個贗品 攻擊倒是有模有樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅熾焰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:17:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我的心還會為過去的幻影而動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗之遺跡 愛與憎恨之門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那個時候拿了我老爸的聖衣石回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了我老爸之後那麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我會向你道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就會為自己的天真而後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅座的蒼摩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是暗之遺跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩 你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙和阿莉雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 不過他們也一定在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前經常送我花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你一次都沒有問過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正渴望的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說一切都是為了創造沒有悲傷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了我 為了得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直不敢面對我的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你利用了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓父親和母親認可你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直視你的罪孽 被永恆的黑暗所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落入地獄深處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有光之小宇宙的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從暗之影中逃離的光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最適合在黑暗中散發微弱光芒的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何想要逃離黑暗而發光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的光芒太礙眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就能在黑暗中得到安詳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在這暗之遺跡中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝視自己的罪孽 接受懲罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是 哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何 覺得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這裡是與你正相稱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問你的小宇宙吧 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:21:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 我的小宇宙是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小宇宙的真正屬性是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要奪回阿莉雅的光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強加雅典娜之名的阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想著和阿莉雅一起走向未來的伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命的利刃指向了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這思念交錯的三個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 年輕的聖鬥士們向命運發起挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途的終焉！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的光芒與年輕的戰士們！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
